lishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2757296194/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2757296194","tinyui":"/x/QgBZp","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2757296194","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2757296194/Archived+Initiatives","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2757296194"}},{"id":"2685665304","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/2685665304","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMjY4NTY2NTMwNA==","status":"current","title":"Preautorizaciones en VPOS PCI","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":172683952},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2685665304/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2685665304/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2685665304/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2685665304/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2685665304","tinyui":"/x/GAAUo","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2685665304","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2685665304/Preautorizaciones+en+VPOS+PCI","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2685665304"}}],"macroRenderedOutput":{},"body":{"storage":{"value":"<p>Requerimientos: <a href=\"https://jira.bancardnet.dom/confluence/display/PRYVPOS2/Especificaciones+vPOS-PCI\">https://jira.bancardnet.dom/confluence/display/PRYVPOS2/Especificaciones+vPOS-PCI</a></p><h2>Introducci&oacute;n</h2><p>Se desea incorporar la funcionalidad de Preautorizaciones en los servicios de VPOS PCI. Para ello, es necesario agregar nuevos servicios, tanto en la creaci&oacute;n de una pre-autorizaci&oacute;n como en la confirmaci&oacute;n de la misma.</p><h2>Datos para seguimiento</h2><p>Estimaci&oacute;n: 120hrs</p><p>Fecha inicio: TBD</p><p>Fecha fin: TBD</p><p>Qubika Jira: TBD</p><h2>Equipo</h2><p>Gesti&oacute;n: <ac:link><ri:user ri:account-id=\"61c0869ff3037f006939b7e3\" /></ac:link>  </p><p>Desarrollo: <ac:link><ri:user ri:account-id=\"612e2e8063f7bb006976b761\" /></ac:link> </p><h2>Tasking:</h2><ol start=\"1\"><li><p>Un nuevo servicio para retornar la info de una card dado un pan encriptado.</p></li><li><p>Modificar el servicio pay_pci_encrypted_buy para recibir un flag si es preautorizacion o no. Si es una preautorizaci&oacute;n, hay que llamar al flujo de Preautorizaciones (business::preautorizations.create). Agregar en external-services el nuevo endpoint de jpos.</p></li><li><p>En preautorization service, hacer un nuevo endpoint (confirm_pci). Tomar como referencia &ldquo;confirm&rdquo;. Llamar a un nuevo servicio de jpos. Agregar en la tabla operations una columna de cantidad de reintentos. Solo se puede reintentar el confirm si la preautorizaci&oacute;n fue fallida. En caso de exceder una cantidad X (configurable) de reintentas, directamente no se le deja reintentar mas. En este &uacute;ltimo caso, devolver un nuevo error.</p></li><li><p>Hoy en dia ya usa pci_buy/rollback. En caso de ser una preautorizaci&oacute;n (pendiente) para un shop_process_id, indicar al jpos con una flag que es una preauth.</p></li></ol>","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/2682323025"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":395282059},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2682323025/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2682323025/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2682323025/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2682323025/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2682323025","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2682323025/Estimaci+n+-+Preautorizaciones+en+VPOS+PCI","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2682323025","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2682323025","tinyui":"/x/UQDhnw","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki"}}